*   [Retsina](/Retsina) – A distinctive [Greek wine](/Greek_wine) flavored with [Aleppo pine](/Pinus_halepensis) [resin](/Resin), a culinary application of [pine](/Pine) exudates.
*   [Russia leather](/Russia_leather) – A water-resistant [leather](/Leather) traditionally curried after [tanning](/Tanning) with a [birch oil](/Birch_oil) distillate, possessing properties somewhat analogous to [turpentine](/Turpentine).